HEADWORD: Resetter
<hw>Re*set"ter</hw> <pr>(-t?r)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Scots
Law)</fld> <def>One who receives or conceals, as stolen goods or
criminal.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Resetter</ent>⟦br⟧

