HEADWORD: Resetter
<hw>Re*set"ter</hw> <pr>(r?-S?t"t?r)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who
resets, or sets again.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Resettle</ent>⟦br⟧
